original: Jönsson, Olga Ellen Maria, tandläkare, Vetlanda, f. 28/9/99 i Uppåkra, Malmöh. 1., av Otto J. o. Maria Persson. — Stud.-ex. v. Lunds fullst. lä-rov. f. fl. 19, med. kand. 24, tandl. 27. Assist, i Vetlanda 27-28, prakt, där sed. 28.
translated: Jönsson, Olga Ellen Maria, dentist, Vetlanda, born 28/9/99 in Uppåkra, Malmöhus. First child of Otto J. and Maria Persson. Graduated from Lund's full high school in 1919, completed medical studies in 1924, and became a dentist in 1927. Worked as an assistant in Vetlanda from 1927-28, and has had her own practice there since 1928.
